description: For hand churned creamy frozen goodness, Fifty licks gourmet ice cream is the place to go. In fact, this mobile ice cream parlor is so popular that pints of their ice cream can be purchased at select grocery stores. Whether it's a hot day or you're just in the mood for a delicious  dessert, Fifty Licks is the perfect place for a frozen treat that everyone will be sure to enjoy.
name: Fifty Licks
